📈 Stock Dashboard (Final Year Project)

🚀 Overview

The Stock Dashboard is a real-time financial analytics web application that helps users analyze stock market data using interactive visualizations and technical indicators.

This project is developed as a Final Year Project, focusing on data analysis, machine learning, and financial insights.

---

🎯 Features

- 📊 Real-time stock data visualization
- 📉 Technical indicators (RSI, MACD, EMA, SMA)
- 📈 Interactive charts and dashboard
- 🤖 Machine Learning-based predictions
- ⚡ Fast and responsive UI using Streamlit

---

🛠️ Tech Stack

- Frontend: Streamlit
- Backend: Python
- Libraries: Pandas, NumPy, Plotly, yFinance, TA
- ML Models: Scikit-learn / XGBoost

---

⚙️ Installation & Setup

1️⃣ Clone the Repository

git clone https://github.com/kanishk-28/StockDashboard-Final-year.git
cd StockDashboard-Final-year

2️⃣ Install Dependencies

pip install -r requirements.txt

3️⃣ Run the Application

streamlit run app.py

